pose, each party shall return or destroy the other's Confidential Information except for one copy that may be retained for legal or regulatory record-keeping.\n\n## Governing Law and Jurisdiction\n\nThis Agreement is governed by the laws of England and Wales and the parties submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of that jurisdiction.\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\nNo Party may assign without the other's prior written consent. This Agreement may be executed in counterparts including by electronic signature. The Agreement contains the entire understanding between the parties in relation to its subject matter and supersedes any prior arrangement or representation.",
